txt.en: Kala-gijak look-outs can be found in the archer towers in Kala-gijak.\n\nYou should defeat Kala-gijak look-outs.
Faeron can be found outside Kala-gijak.\n\nYou should talk to Faeron.

'Do you see those archer towers around Kala-gijak's perimeter? There is a look-out posted in each one. I need you to climb up and prevent those Uruks from signaling the alarm. Otherwise, our whole plan may fail.'
'Excellent. Now when we attack, they won't see it coming. Everything is going according to plan.'
Kala-gijak has archer towers all around the perimeter where look-outs search for intruders. You need to find a way to remove these look-outs before your Dr√∫adan friends are spotted.
